### ============================================
### COURSE FILTERS & SORTING TESTING
### ============================================
### Test the course filtering and sorting API
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminEmail = sharma@amu.ac.in
@adminPassword = Teacher@123
@token = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. LOGIN AS ADMIN (Get Token First)
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### Copy the token from response and replace @token above

### ============================================
### 2. GET ALL COURSES (No Filters)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: All courses returned

### ============================================
### 3. FILTER BY BRANCH (COBEA)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?branch=COBEA
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Only COBEA courses

### ============================================
### 4. FILTER BY SEMESTER (Semester 3)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?semester=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Only semester 3 courses

### ============================================
### 5. FILTER BY COURSE TYPE (Theory)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?courseType=Theory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Only theory courses

### ============================================
### 6. FILTER BY COURSE TYPE (Lab)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?courseType=Lab
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Only lab courses

### ============================================
### 7. FILTER CORE COURSES ONLY
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?isElective=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Only core (non-elective) courses

### ============================================
### 8. FILTER ELECTIVE COURSES ONLY
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?isElective=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Only elective courses

### ============================================
### 9. FILTER BY ELECTIVE GROUP
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?isElective=true&electiveGroup=ELEC-3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Only elective courses in ELEC-3 group

### ============================================
### 10. FILTER BY CREDITS RANGE (3-4 credits)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?minCredits=3&maxCredits=4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Courses with 3-4 credits

### ============================================
### 11. FILTER BY MINIMUM CREDITS (4+)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?minCredits=4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Courses with 4 or more credits

### ============================================
### 12. FILTER BY MAXIMUM CREDITS (2 or less)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/teacher/courses?maxCredits=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: Courses with 2 or fewer credits

